AT|

This very valuable echo has now been extended. (At just what point during the 24 year period the extension became widespread we cannot say—perhaps the early Forties.) The defending player following suit with his low cards echoes with either ^*Itwo or four^*N cards in the suit. This enables the Partner to get valuable information much more rapidly in many cases. Let’s look at this situation [Examples A and B].|
